{"data":[{"date":"09:25 05/08","title":"Xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp tr\u1eadn U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/xem-truc-tiep-tran-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-oman-o-dau.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp tr\u00ean k\u00eanh VTV6 nh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ec7, thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 NHM s\u1ebd xem tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y qua k\u00eanh VTV5 c\u1ee7a \u0110TH Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</h2><h2>Tr\u1eadn U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng tr\u00ean VTV6</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h30 t\u1ed1i nay, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf c\u00fap Vinaphone 2018 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nDo tr\u00f9ng gi\u1edd v\u1edbi l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf gi\u1ea3i b\u00f3ng chuy\u1ec1n n\u1eef VTV Cup 2018 n\u00ean thay v\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp tr\u00ean k\u00eanh VTV6 nh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ec7, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e0i truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh Vi\u1ec7t Nam ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng tr\u00ean k\u00eanh VTV5.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/Xem-truc-tiep-U23-Viet-Nam-vs-U23-Oman-o-dau-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa&nbsp;U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp tr\u00ean k\u00eanh VTV5</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c gi\u1eefa Uzbekistan vs Palestine c\u0169ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e1t tr\u00ean k\u00eanh n\u00e0y do k\u00eanh VTV6 ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng chuy\u1ec1n n\u1eef gi\u1eef \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1edbi \u0110T n\u1eef Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c tr\u00f9ng th\u1eddi gian di\u1ec5n ra c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i VTV Cup n\u00ean lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu U23 Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018 c\u0169ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp tr\u00ean k\u00eanh VTV5. Ngo\u00e0i ra, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/\" target=\"_blank\">Bongda24h </span>c\u0169ng s\u1ebd c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn, k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf gi\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p>M\u1eddi b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc ch\u00fa \u00fd theo d\u00f5i.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Li\u00ean quan t\u1edbi c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam cho tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Oman t\u1ed1i nay, chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua 4/8, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp nh\u1eb9 trong khu\u00f4n vi\u00ean trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a VFF. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp n\u00e0y, 11 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng Cup 2018 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho t\u1eadp ri\u00eang. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, HLV Park Hang Seo cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed1i kh\u00e1ng chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea5u Oman. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n gi\u1eefa U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 U23 Palestine.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd b\u1edfi&nbsp;tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3&nbsp;chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c&nbsp;\u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u1eb1m t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng nh\u1ea5t.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/lo-doi-hinh-ra-san-tran-viet-nam-oman-bui-tien-dung-bat-chinh-minh-vuong-giu-bang-thu-quan-168-193753.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/lo-doi-hinh-ra-san-tran-viet-nam-oman-bui-tien-dung-bat-chinh-minh-vuong-giu-bang-thu-quan.JPG\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/lo-doi-hinh-ra-san-tran-viet-nam-oman-bui-tien-dung-bat-chinh-minh-vuong-giu-bang-thu-quan-168-193753.html\">L\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n tr\u1eadn Vi\u1ec7t Nam &ndash; Oman: B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh, Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng gi\u1eef b\u0103ng th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n?</span><br />\r\nTheo m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ngu\u1ed3n tin, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh c\u00f2n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1ebd gi\u1eef b\u0103ng th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-oman-19h30-ngay-058-co-hoi-cho-kep-phu-168-193749.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/nhan-dinh-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-oman-19h30-ngay-058-co-hoi-cho-kep-phu.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-oman-19h30-ngay-058-co-hoi-cho-kep-phu-168-193749.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman (19h30, ng\u00e0y 05/8): C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho k\u00e9p ph\u1ee5</span><br />\r\nV\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h30 t\u1ed1i nay 5/8, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 hai t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng U23 Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf gi\u1eefa U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra. V\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eefng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:11.5pt;font-family:\" new=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5106","checkdouble":"193758"},{"date":"09:47 05/08","title":"C\u1ef1u HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1ec9 ra ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/5/cuu-hlv-truong-dt-viet-nam-chi-ra-nguoi-da-cap-tot-nhat-voi-cong-phuong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palestine h\u00f4m 3/8 v\u1eeba qua, c\u1ef1u thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam, \u00f4ng Tr\u1ea7n B\u00ecnh S\u1ef1 cho r\u1eb1ng Anh \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o.</h2><h2>HLV Tr\u1ea7n B\u00ecnh S\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9 ra ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u00fa l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palestine \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf h\u00f4m 3/8. \u1ede tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Anh \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 v\u00e0 m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 mang v\u1ec1 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ch\u00ednh HLV Tr\u1ea7n B\u00ecnh S\u1ef1 c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn Anh \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o nh\u1ea5t l\u00fac n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u00e0 HLV Park Hang Seo n\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Tr\u1ea7n B\u00ecnh S\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9 ra ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Tr\u1ea7n B\u00ecnh S\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9 ra ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/HLV-Tran-Binh-Su-chi-ra-nguoi-da-cap-tot-nhat-voi-Cong-Phuong-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <div class=\"imagecontainer\" style=\"width: 779px;\">\r\n            <table style=\"text-align: center; width: 777px;\">\r\n                <tbody>\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                        <td><em>Anh \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c tin c\u1eady c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean b\u00e1o Th\u1ec3 thao V\u0103n h\u00f3a, \u00f4ng S\u1ef1 \u2018g\u1ed7\u2019 nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t: \u201cH\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf th\u00ec y\u00ean t\u00e2m r\u1ed3i. Theo t\u00f4i, Anh \u0110\u1ee9c l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft nh\u1ea5t cho \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n b\u00e2y gi\u1edd v\u00e0 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p v\u1edbi C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Anh \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1t, kinh nghi\u1ec7m d\u00e0y d\u1ea1n. Khi g\u1eb7p c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1t th\u00ec anh ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef3 \u0111\u00e8, l\u00e0m t\u01b0\u1eddng, h\u00fat h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec3 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f3 kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, HLV Park Hang Seo th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p gi\u1eefa Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ghi nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n. C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u1edbi Anh \u0110\u1ee9c l\u00e0 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. Anh \u0110\u1ee9c m\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1 v\u1edbi \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee3p l\u00fd \u0111\u00e2u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh \u0111\u00e1 v\u1edbi C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee3p l\u00fd b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e2u v\u00ec kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 so b\u00ec v\u1edbi Anh \u0110\u1ee9c. Khi c\u1ea7n lui v\u1ec1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, Anh \u0110\u1ee9c c\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u00e0m r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y\u201d.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-oman-19h30-ngay-058-co-hoi-cho-kep-phu-168-193749.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/nhan-dinh-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-oman-19h30-ngay-058-co-hoi-cho-kep-phu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-oman-19h30-ngay-058-co-hoi-cho-kep-phu-168-193749.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman (19h30, ng\u00e0y 05/8): C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho k\u00e9p ph\u1ee5</span><br>\r\nV\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h30 t\u1ed1i nay 5/8, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 hai t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng U23 Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf gi\u1eefa U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra. V\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eefng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng Tr\u1ea7n B\u00ecnh S\u1ef1 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u2018tay ngh\u1ec1\u2019 c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo khi x\u00e1o tr\u1ed9n s\u1ed1 \u00e1o \u1edf \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf vi\u1ec7c b\u1ecb c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 b\u1eaft b\u00e0i m\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f2n l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c g\u00e2y \u00e1p l\u1ef1c, bu\u1ed9c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c b\u1edfi kh\u00f4ng ai bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ec1 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu n\u00e0y, HLV Tr\u1ea7n B\u00ecnh S\u1ef1 cho r\u1eb1ng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd \u0111o\u1ea1t ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf \u0111ang c\u00f3 khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra l\u00fac 19h30 t\u1ed1i nay v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt tr\u00ean VTV5. M\u1eddi b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc ch\u00fa \u00fd theo d\u00f5i.</p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/3/Highlight-Viet-Nam-vs-Palestine-.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:\n115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5105","checkdouble":"193760"},{"date":"10:10 05/08","title":"HLV Real Madrid ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Modric","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/11/hlv-lopetegui-noi-ve-tuong-lai-modric.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Lopetegui n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Modric. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 51 tu\u1ed5i nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh Real Madrid kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u00e0i hoa n\u00e0y ra \u0111i trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai g\u1ea7n.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Modric b\u1ecb s\u0103n \u0111\u00f3n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u0103m 2018 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Luka Modric \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao c\u1ea3 t\u1ea1i CLB v\u00e0 \u0110TQG. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Real Madrid, anh gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League. L\u00ean \u0110T Croatia, Modric ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng, gi\u00fap h\u1ecd v\u00e0o t\u1edbi chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1 nh\u00e2n Modric th\u00f4ng qua nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u0111\u1ec9nh cao \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea7u ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0 C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i. Qua \u0111\u00f3, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 32 tu\u1ed5i nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb c\u00e1c t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 Inter Milan.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Lopetegui n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Modric h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Lopetegui n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Modric h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/HLV-Lopetegui-noi-ve-tuong-lai-Modric-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Modric t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nInter quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Luka Modric. HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng Luciano Spalletti c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1eafc n\u1ecbch \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Nh\u01b0ng Real kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Juventus t\u1ea1i International Champions Cup t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9, HLV Julen Lopetegui n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Modric. \u00d4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ef1u ng\u00f4i sao Tottenham s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Santiago Bernabeu trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center;\" width=\"779\" height=\"357\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Modric\" title=\"tien ve Modric\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/11/hlv-lopetegui-noi-ve-tuong-lai-modric.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>HLV Lopetegui n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Modric</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 ng\u00e0i ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean quan \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd ki\u1ebfn g\u00ec kh\u00e1c\u201d, Lopetegui n\u00f3i trong m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o. \u201cLuka Modric l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 phi th\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u00f3n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1edbi v\u00f2ng tay r\u1ed9ng m\u1edf. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi Modric sau k\u1ef3 World Cup tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p nhau khi Modric tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Madrid v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng xem li\u1ec7u c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u (v\u1edbi Atletico Madrid \u0111\u00eam 15/8) hay kh\u00f4ng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t y\u00eau th\u00edch v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t vui n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y Modric s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u00e0 s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.\u201d<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-dua-ra-quyet-dinh-co-mua-them-tien-dao-hay-khong-180-193677.html\">Real \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 mua th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o hay kh\u00f4ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/courtois-se-roi-chelsea-cap-ben-real-o-he-2018-172-193672.html\">Courtois s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Chelsea c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Real \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/ac-milan-hoi-mua-mateo-kovacic-176-193644.html\">Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh sao Real v\u1edbi M.U v\u00e0 Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-ra-gia-modric-cho-cac-doi-tac-180-192606.html\">V\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y, M.U v\u00e0 Inter c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mang Modric r\u1eddi Real</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/nong-hlv-real-bat-ngo-che-thibaut-courtois-180-192594.html\">N\u00f3ng: HLV Real b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u201cch\u00ea\u201d Thibaut Courtois</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5104","checkdouble":"193761"},{"date":"09:09 05/08","title":"Arsenal kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/emery-xac-nhan-monreal-chan-thuong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Emery x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Monreal ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y d\u1eabn t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Arsenal c\u1ee7a chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i n\u00e0y cho giai \u0111o\u1ea1n kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>V\u1ea5n n\u1ea1n ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Chelsea trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y, Sead Kolasinac \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111au ch\u00e2n tr\u00e1i. Anh bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi s\u00e2n s\u1edbm \u1edf ph\u00fat 70 nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho Ainsley Maitland-Niles.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 x\u00e9t nghi\u1ec7m ch\u1ec9 ra Kolasinac s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i trong \u00edt nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 2 th\u00e1ng t\u1edbi. Ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft, Arsenal m\u1edbi nh\u1eadn tin d\u1eef t\u1eeb Nacho Monreal. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y m\u1edbi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eeb World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Emery x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Monreal ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Emery x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Monreal ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/emery-xac-nhan-monreal-chan-thuong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Emery x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Monreal ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Emery x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u00ednh Emery x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Monreal ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Arsenal kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng k\u1ecbp tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i trong tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League v\u1edbi Man City l\u00fac 22h ng\u00e0y 12/8 t\u1edbi v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho Maitland-Niles.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cMonreal kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i m\u00e0 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi HLV th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng th\u1ee9 3 t\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i\u201d, Emery n\u00f3i v\u1edbi ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean.\u00a0 <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i d\u0129 nhi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng x\u1ea3y ra. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t kh\u1ea3 kh\u00e1ng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i mu\u1ed9n sau khi d\u1ef1 World Cup nh\u01b0 Montreal v\u00e0 c\u0169ng g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1edbi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y k\u1ecbp d\u1ef1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Manchester City.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u00fap Maitland-Niles th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0y. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Sau \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin t\u1eeb c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng.\u201d<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Arsenal tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tan-binh-ngoai-hang-anh-muon-gianh-hang-hot-world-cup-voi-arsenal-va-liverpool-172-193730.html\">T\u00e2n binh Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh h\u00e0ng hot World Cup v\u1edbi Arsenal v\u00e0 Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/roma-bat-ngo-muon-rut-ruot-arsenal-172-193727.html\">Roma b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n r\u00fat ru\u1ed9t Arsenal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/roma-bat-ngo-muon-rut-ruot-arsenal-172-193727.html\">Roma b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n r\u00fat ru\u1ed9t Arsenal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/kolasinac-chan-thuong-nghi-10-tuan-172-193693.html\">Tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Arsenal ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng, ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u 10 tu\u1ea7n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/muc-tieu-so-1-cua-arsenal-dat-duoc-thoa-thuan-voi-roma-172-192633.html\">M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi Roma</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5103","checkdouble":"193754"},{"date":"09:45 05/08","title":"Smalling kh\u00f4ng th\u00e8m \u0111\u1ebfm x\u1ec9a \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c MU mua th\u00eam trung v\u1ec7","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/smalling-khong-them-dem-xia-den-viec-mu-mua-them-trung-ve.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chris Smalling t\u1ef1 tin r\u1ea7ng anh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Man United, b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 Toby Alderweireld, Harry Maguire hay Yerry Mina.</h2><h2>Smalling t\u1ef1 tin v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \u1edf MU</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t  trung v\u1ec7 v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Eric Bailly v\u00e0 Victor  Lindelof trong 2 m\u00f9a h\u00e8 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn \u0111ang ch\u1edd  \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u  th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng minh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00edch nghi l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c v\u1edbi c\u00e1c  \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Smalling kh\u00f4ng th\u00e8m \u0111\u1ebfm x\u1ec9a \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c MU mua th\u00eam trung v\u1ec7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Smalling kh\u00f4ng th\u00e8m \u0111\u1ebfm x\u1ec9a \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c MU mua th\u00eam trung v\u1ec7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/smalling-khong-them-dem-xia-den-viec-mu-mua-them-trung-ve.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Smalling kh\u00f4ng th\u00e8m \u0111\u1ebfm x\u1ec9a \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c MU mua th\u00eam trung v\u1ec7</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00e2n binh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea9y Smalling kh\u1ecfi  v\u1ecb tr\u00ed xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t. G\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tin \u0111\u1ed3n li\u00ean h\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i sao 28 tu\u1ed5i  v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi th\u0103ng h\u1ea1ng l\u00ean Premier League l\u00e0 Wolves. Nh\u01b0ng tuy\u1ec3n  th\u1ee7 Anh \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb th\u1eb3ng th\u1eafn v\u1ec1 mong mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Old Trafford.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cC\u00f3  c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf Man United kh\u00e1 l\u00e2u. Nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c ra qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00f3  v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eafm. Th\u1eadt \u0111i\u00ean r\u1ed3 n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n ng\u1ed3i l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 khi m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9  b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u, nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. M\u1ecdi th\u1ee9  th\u1eadt \u0111i\u00ean r\u1ed3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y ph\u00fat hi\u1ec7n  t\u1ea1i. V\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng n\u0103m t\u1edbi, t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u1edb v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc  n\u00e0y v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cHy v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c  nhi\u1ec1u th\u00e0nh t\u1ef1u h\u01a1n n\u1eefa. Th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t khi t\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn v\u00e0 \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y  m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c HLV \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t ch\u00e2n t\u1edbi  \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i lu\u00f4n c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng l\u00e0m nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y\u201d.</em><br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>MU t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Smalling  \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n 289 l\u1ea7n cho Man United k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng  1/2010. T\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Old Trafford, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 8 danh  hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 2 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 Smalling \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u kh\u00e1 t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i Premier League b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u1edfi tranh v\u00e0o tu\u1ea7n sau.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i  ngh\u0129 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi \u1edf Premier League \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u00e1 nhanh. Nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng \u1edf  Manchester United l\u00e0 v\u1eady. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafc t\u1edbi  kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u. V\u1eady n\u00ean vi\u1ec7c ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n  cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5102","checkdouble":"193757"},{"date":"10:03 05/08","title":"Sarri: \"Chelsea c\u1ea7n Jorginho h\u01a1n Man City\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/sarri-chelsea-can-jorginho-hon-man-city.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Sarri t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 vui m\u1eebng khi c\u01b0\u1edbp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Jorginho t\u1eeb tay Man City v\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thu h\u1eb9p kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.</h2><h2>Chelsea n\u1eabng tay tr\u00ean Jorginho c\u1ee7a Man City</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/morata-chelsea-may-man-vi-chieu-mo-duoc-jorginho-172-193690.html\" target=\"_blank\">Jorginho</span> \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1ebd gia nh\u1eadp Man City. Nh\u01b0ng vi\u1ec7c Chelsea b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV Sarri \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Italia \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed 55 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPep Guardiola r\u1ea5t kh\u00f4ng vui khi m\u1ea5t Jorginho d\u00f9 \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u0103m tia c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y t\u1eeb l\u00e2u. Nh\u01b0ng HLV Sarri tin r\u1eb1ng Chelsea l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ea7n Jorginho h\u01a1n Man City khi kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1eefa 2 \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 30 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jorginho\" title=\"Jorginho\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/sarri-chelsea-can-jorginho-hon-man-city.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Sarri cho r\u1eb1ng Chelsea c\u1ea7n Jorginho h\u01a1n Man City</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>&ldquo;T\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y v\u1edbi Guardiola v\u00e0o Ch\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt. Jorginho l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 thu h\u1eb9p kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. Ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n Jorginho h\u01a1n Man City. V\u1eady n\u00ean vi\u1ec7c Jorginho t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn. Pep \u0111ang c\u00f3 trong tay nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. Fernandinho l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t. B\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng Premier League m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00f3i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i r\u1eb1ng kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1eefa 2 \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00e0 30 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i thu h\u1eb9p con s\u1ed1 30 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3. V\u00e0 t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch l\u00e0 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u1eadt l\u1ef1c. C\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 l\u00e0 m\u1ecdi v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft ch\u1ec9 th\u00f4ng qua c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng&rdquo;.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Sarri nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap Anh</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a HLV Sarri v\u1edbi c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb HLV Chelsea s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n Pep Guardiola \u1edf Si\u00eau c\u00fap Anh. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Sarri c\u0169ng t\u1eebng c\u00f3 d\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Pep khi c\u00f2n d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Napoli. V\u00e0 Sarri t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 d\u00e8 ch\u1eebng tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e0n ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>&ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 cho b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Man City. T\u00f4i t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Man City v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 11 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0 h\u1ecd ch\u01a1i hay nh\u1ea5t. V\u00e0 m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. 20 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u01a1n \u00e1c m\u1ed9ng (Napoli \u0111\u1ec3 thua 0-2 ngay sau 14 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn)&rdquo;.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap Anh:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhan-dinh-chelsea-vs-man-city-sieu-cup-anh-21h00-ngay-58-ra-ngo-gap-nui-172-193739.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea vs Man City (Si\u00eau C\u00fap Anh, 21h00 ng\u00e0y 5/8): Ra ng\u00f5 g\u1eb7p n\u00fai</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-cau-hoi-danh-cho-sarri-truoc-tran-tranh-sieu-cup-voi-man-city-172-193661.html\">3 c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi d\u00e0nh cho Sarri tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau c\u00fap v\u1edbi Man City</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5101","checkdouble":"193762"},{"date":"10:24 05/08","title":"MU \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi sao Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/5/mu-dat-duoc-thoa-thuan-ca-nhan-voi-mina.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Man United \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi Yerry Mina c\u1ee7a Barcelona.</h2><h2>MU c\u00f3 b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfn l\u1edbn v\u1ee5 Mina\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"V\u1ee5 MU chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Mina Hai b\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"V\u1ee5 MU chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Mina Hai b\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/mu-dat-duoc-thoa-thuan-ca-nhan-voi-mina.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>MU \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi Mina</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Jose Mourinho mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a trung v\u1ec7 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m Toby Alderweireld v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Old Trafford. Nh\u01b0ng Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u1ecf ra t\u1edbi 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0 l\u1eddi y\u00eau c\u1ea7u t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Spurs.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Man United v\u1eabn \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Tottenham v\u1ec1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Alderweireld. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a trung v\u1ec7 Yerry Mina c\u1ee7a Barca v\u1ec1 th\u00e0nh Manchester.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 theo t\u1edd Mundo Deportivo, Man \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 5 n\u0103m. Mina s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 7.5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u1ed7i n\u0103m, t\u1ee9c x\u1ea5p x\u1ec9 145.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc thu\u1ebf. Con s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y cao h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n so v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Mina t\u1ea1i Barca c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea1nh tranh Everton \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb.</div>\r\n<h2>MU v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Barca</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 MU\u00a0chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Mina<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mina-bao-tin-vui-cho-mu-172-192357.html\" target=\"_blank\">bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mina-bao-tin-vui-cho-mu-172-192357.html</span> v\u1eabn \u0111ang m\u1eafc \u1edf kho\u1ea3n ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Ngo\u00e0i ra, Man United c\u0169ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i cho Barca n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 lo\u1ea1i Alderweireld kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch chi\u00eau m\u1ed9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMina \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n t\u1ea1i Camp Nou sau khi chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 1. HLV Ernesto Valverde v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a b\u1ecb thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c b\u1edfi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u1eabu v\u1eady, Mina \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Colombia. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u1edf v\u00f2ng knock-out c\u00e0ng l\u00e0m t\u0103ng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m, Barca chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Mina v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 ch\u1ec9 11.5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Nh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 x\u1ee9 Catalonia mong mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u1edbi b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ee9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia. Con s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn Man United ph\u1ea3i c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc b\u1edfi Mina ch\u01b0a ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Man United:</strong><br>\r\n<strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/smalling-khong-them-dem-xia-den-viec-mu-mua-them-trung-ve-172-193757.html\">Smalling kh\u00f4ng th\u00e8m \u0111\u1ebfm x\u1ec9a \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c MU mua th\u00eam trung v\u1ec7</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/muc-tieu-so-1-cua-mu-bi-che-khong-biet-phong-ngu-180-193745.html\">M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a M.U b\u1ecb ch\u00ea kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nXu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5100","checkdouble":"193764"},{"date":"07:07 05/08","title":"Leonardo Bonucci quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng xin l\u1ed7i sau khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/4/leonardo-bonucci-khong-xin-loi-sau-khi-tro-lai-juventus.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Leonardo Bonucci tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng xin l\u1ed7i khi v\u1ea5p ph\u1ea3i s\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Juventus sau qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian phi\u00eau b\u1ea1t sang AC Milan, m\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bonucci tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau m\u1ed9t n\u0103m gia nh\u1eadp AC Milan, Leonardo Bonucci \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Mattia Caldara t\u1edbi Rossoneri. H\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, Bonucci \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u00e3i nhau v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League d\u1eabn t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gia nh\u1eadp AC Milan.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Leonardo Bonucci kh\u00f4ng xin l\u1ed7i sau khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Leonardo Bonucci kh\u00f4ng xin l\u1ed7i sau khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/4/leonardo-bonucci-khong-xin-loi-sau-khi-tro-lai-juventus.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Leonardo Bonucci kh\u00f4ng xin l\u1ed7i sau khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ai c\u0169ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Bonucci, m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7 hay nh\u1ea5t Italia th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. Trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Juventus, nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 t\u1edbi s\u00e2n t\u1eadp, gi\u01a1 l\u00ean nh\u1eefng t\u1ea5m bi\u1ec3u ng\u1eef \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb Bonucci ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i l\u1eddi xin l\u1ed7i c\u00f4ng khai v\u00ec h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng r\u1eddi b\u1ecf \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nhi\u1ec1u C\u0110V Juventus cho r\u1eb1ng Bonucci s\u1edf d\u0129 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus l\u00e0 do AC Milan hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u \u0111i xu\u1ed1ng. C\u1ef1u Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch ng\u01b0\u1eddi Trung Qu\u1ed1c, Li Yonghong \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t quy\u1ec1n ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t AC Milan v\u00e0o tay Elliott Management - Qu\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a Hoa K\u1ef3 do kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 chi tr\u1ea3 kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e3 vay \u0111\u1ec3 mua l\u1ea1i CLB.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng n\u00f3i l\u1eddi xin l\u1ed7i<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c C\u0110V, Leonardo Bonucci kh\u00f4ng xin l\u1ed7i: \"T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd ch\u1ee9ng minh t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bonucci tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi t\u1edbi AC Milan h\u00e8 2017 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u1ea3y n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Juventus, ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 19 b\u00e0n sau 319 tr\u1eadn. Tuy nhi\u00ean, trung v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 nhi\u1ebfc m\u00f3c Dybala trong gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9 gi\u1eefa hai hi\u1ec7p trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League 2016-17 g\u1eb7p Real Madrid d\u1eabn t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i Bonucci, Juventus m\u00f9a n\u00e0y c\u00f2n b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam 4 t\u00e2n binh kh\u00e1c g\u1ed3m th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Mattia Perin, Emre Can, Joao Cancelo v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 si\u00eau sao Cristiano Ronaldo.</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Leonardo Bonucci:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/goc-nhin-tai-hop-cuu-den-juventus-kho-lam-nen-chuyen-o-champions-league-176-193654.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: T\u00e1i h\u1ee3p \u201cc\u1eebu \u0111en\u201d, Juventus kh\u00f3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n \u1edf Champions League</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/bonucci-tro-ve-juventus-day-la-nha-cua-toi-176-192614.html\">Bonucci tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Juventus: \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/juventus-va-ac-milan-sap-trao-doi-bom-tan-176-191928.html\">Juventus v\u00e0 AC Milan s\u1eafp trao \u0111\u1ed5i bom t\u1ea5n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/hlv-gattuso-muon-bonucci-o-lai-milan-176-191897.html\">HLV Milan n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi Bonucci c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 sang M.U ho\u1eb7c Real?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-nhan-don-dau-vu-bonucci-172-191595.html\">MU nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00f2n \u0111au v\u1ee5 sao kh\u1ee7ng Italia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/psg-mu-va-chelsea-dai-chien-vi-bonucci-172-191094.html\">PSG, MU v\u00e0 Chelsea \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec sao kh\u1ee7ng AC Milan</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><br>\r\nN.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5099","checkdouble":"193737"},{"date":"07:18 05/08","title":"Ancelotti b\u1ecf h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/ancelotti-bo-hop-bao-sau-tham-bai-truoc-liverpool.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>B\u1ecb The Kop h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 0-5, HLV Ancelotti chia s\u1ebb sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool, nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng tham gia cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o.\r\n</h2><h2>Thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Napoli b\u1ecf h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u1ea1ng, nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Napoli th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n l\u1ea1i qu\u00e1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. H\u1ecd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng s\u1eadp b\u1eaby ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool, v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn v\u1ec1 t\u1edbi 5 b\u00e0n thua. Sau tr\u1eadn, Ancelotti \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o, v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn Napoli ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u00d4ng \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng tham d\u1ef1 h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o v\u00ec m\u1ed9t l\u00fd do \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n&rdquo; &ndash; \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9, &ldquo;b\u1edfi \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng n\u1eb1m trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch. Ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Ancelotti l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n v\u1edbi Sky Sports, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 trong bu\u1ed5i ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n n\u00e0y, HLV Italia \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng chia s\u1ebb: &ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3. Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1eadm lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn, v\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1edbi 5 b\u00e0n th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0m phi\u1ec1n ch\u00fang t\u00f4i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Ancelotti chia s\u1ebb sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool 0-5 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Ancelotti chia s\u1ebb sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool 0-5 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/ance.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Ancelotti chia s\u1ebb sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Napoli \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1edfi m\u1edf, nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ch\u00e0ng trai \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t hi\u1ec7u su\u1ea5t v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t so v\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 theo k\u1ecbp h\u1ecd. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n v\u00e0 b\u1ecb tr\u1eebng ph\u1ea1t b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng pha ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng &ndash; v\u0169 kh\u00ed m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Liverpool.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ph\u1ea3i m\u1ea5t th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 qu\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ea1o. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Napoli kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ed1ng l\u1ea1i h\u1ecd, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng&rdquo; &ndash; HLV Carlo Ancelotti chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn thua Liverpool.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, Napoli s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam 2 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu n\u1eefa v\u1edbi Dortmund v\u00e0 Wolfsburg, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Lazio v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 18/8.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/5/Liverpool-vs-Napoli.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/alisson-ra-mat-thanh-cong-klopp-noi-gi-172-193744.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/alisson-ra-mat-thanh-cong-klopp-noi-gi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/alisson-ra-mat-thanh-cong-klopp-noi-gi-172-193744.html\">Alisson ra m\u1eaft th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, Klopp n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span><br>\r\nTrong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ho\u00e0nh tr\u00e1ng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 5-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Napoli, HLV Jurgen Klopp h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 Alisson &ndash; bom t\u1ea5n 67 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-liverpool-50-napoli-giao-huu-clb-he-2018-329-193740.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/video-tong-hop-liverpool-50-napoli-giao-huu-clb-he-2018.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-liverpool-50-napoli-giao-huu-clb-he-2018-329-193740.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Liverpool 5-0 Napoli (Giao h\u1eefu CLB h\u00e8 2018)</span><br>\r\nTh\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi trong l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m b\u1edfi \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ebfn cu\u1ed1i v\u00e0...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5098","checkdouble":"193747"},{"date":"07:50 05/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman (19h30, ng\u00e0y 05/8): C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho k\u00e9p ph\u1ee5","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/nhan-dinh-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-oman-19h30-ngay-058-co-hoi-cho-kep-phu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h30 t\u1ed1i nay 5/8, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 hai t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng U23 Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf gi\u1eefa U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra. V\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u00f3 d\u1ecbp th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 ghi \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi BHL c\u00f9ng HLV Park Hang Seo.</h2><h2>Ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n kh\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman t\u1ed1i nay, HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m nh\u1eefng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t trong danh s\u00e1ch \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh, V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c,\u2026 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m r\u1ea1ng danh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m nay hay l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t m\u1edbi nh\u01b0 Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng, H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng, Tri\u1ec7u Vi\u1ec7t H\u01b0ng. 10 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 ng\u1ed3i tr\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111ang c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u. V\u00e0 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ai \u0111i, ai \u1edf l\u1ea1i sau ng\u00e0y 7/8 t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman (19h30, ng\u00e0y 058) C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman (19h30, ng\u00e0y 058) C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/Nhan-dinh-U23-Viet-Nam-vs-U23-Oman-(19h30,-ngay-058)-Co-hoi-cho-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Tr\u1eadn\u00a0U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c 'k\u00e9p ph\u1ee5' tr\u1ed5 t\u00e0i</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, anh ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng th\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd. T\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 l\u00e0 Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c, m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o SLNA, s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tung v\u00e0o s\u00e2n.\u00a0Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ph\u1ecfng \u0111o\u00e1n b\u1edfi th\u1ea7y Park lu\u00f4n t\u1ea1o b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u00e0o ph\u00fat ch\u00f3t v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ea5u Oman, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 m\u1ea1nh v\u1ec1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng\u00a0bi\u00ean, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tranh ch\u1ea5p. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u01b0u \u00fd \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng pha kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn, khi m\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u cao \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman c\u0169ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i U23 c\u1ee7a hai n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u nhau. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam (tham d\u1ef1 v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch l\u00e0 \u0110TQG) \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng g\u1eb7p \u0110TQG Oman \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ecd x\u00e1t \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00edch l\u0169y kinh nghi\u1ec7m, trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i Asian Cup 2004. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi \u0111\u00f3, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua \u1edf c\u1ea3 hai l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111i v\u00e0 v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 l\u00e0 0-6 v\u00e0 0-2. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd, b\u1edfi c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Oman v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1ec1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a 14 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 l\u00fac n\u00e0y b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc, khi ch\u00fang ta \u0111ang l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 \u00c1 qu\u00e2n U23 ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c. Do \u0111\u00f3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ef1 tin, b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh v\u00e0 khai th\u00e1c t\u1ed1t nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd g\u1eb7t h\u00e1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 m\u00ecnh mong mu\u1ed1n.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u23-viet-nam-da-lo-ra-nhung-van-de-dac-biet-o-he-thong-phong-thu-168-193719.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/u23-viet-nam-da-lo-ra-nhung-van-de-dac-biet-o-he-thong-phong-thu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u23-viet-nam-da-lo-ra-nhung-van-de-dac-biet-o-he-thong-phong-thu-168-193719.html\">\u201cU23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ed9 ra nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7\u201d</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Palestine, HLV k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Vinh cho r\u1eb1ng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn c\u00f2n b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 nhi\u1ec1u h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 trong...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt n\u00e0o?<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, U23 Oman \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 U23 Uzbekistan trong cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi. Do \u0111\u00f3, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ch\u1ee7 quan \u1edf cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n U23 Oman trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh khi gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng A v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iran 2-0 v\u00e0 5-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Kyrgyzstan (ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1). Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u00ec (3-2), Jordan (2-1) v\u00e0 2 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 0-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Cameroon v\u00e0 2-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palestine.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tr\u1ea3i qua 90 ph\u00fat kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. Thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh v\u1eeba tr\u00e1nh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, tr\u00e1nh l\u1ed9 b\u00e0i, song \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt l\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00f3a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Trung \u0110\u00f4ng lu\u00f4n m\u1ea1nh \u1edf l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u00f9ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ch\u1ee7 quan, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman (19h30, ng\u00e0y 058) C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman (19h30, ng\u00e0y 058) C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/Nhan-dinh-U23-Viet-Nam-vs-U23-Oman-(19h30,-ngay-058)-Co-hoi-cho-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>R\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c trung th\u00e0nh v\u1edbi s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 3-5-2 t\u1ea1i U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 3-5-2 trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n. B\u1ed9 ba trung v\u1ec7 Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, Duy M\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t. Trong s\u1ed1 5 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t so v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 V\u0103n Thanh (ph\u1ea3i), V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft, Quang H\u1ea3i v\u00e0 V\u0103n H\u1eadu (tr\u00e1i). Anh \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng.\u00a0<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i n\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Oman c\u00f3 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 Palestine. Tuy nhi\u00ean, s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng thay \u0111\u1ed5i nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 nh\u1eb1m th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ra \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1i \u01b0u. Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng nhi\u1ec1u g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb ho\u1eb7c th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng Park. B\u1edfi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Mr. Park s\u1ebd \u0111\u1eb7t nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m l\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0, U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1eeb l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 nh\u00e0 cho t\u1edbi s\u1ef1 th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft, nhi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed9, th\u1ee9c \u0103n. V\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ra s\u00e2n v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3o gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng v\u00e0 NHM.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa\u00a0<o:p></o:p>U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h30 t\u1ed1i nay. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, hai \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n U23 Uzbekistan v\u00e0 Palestine s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p nhau \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra l\u00fac 16h30. Mong b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u00f3n xem.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bi-cam-hoa-ngay-ra-quan-hlv-uzbekistan-gui-loi-thach-thuc-toi-u23-viet-nam-168-193695.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/4/bi-cam-hoa-ngay-ra-quan-hlv-uzbekistan-gui-loi-thach-thuc-toi-u23-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bi-cam-hoa-ngay-ra-quan-hlv-uzbekistan-gui-loi-thach-thuc-toi-u23-viet-nam-168-193695.html\">B\u1ecb c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, HLV Uzbekistan g\u1eedi l\u1eddi th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c t\u1edbi U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a kh\u00f4ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Oman,  HLV \u0111\u1ed9i U23 Uzbekistan \u0111\u00e3 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-giao-huu-u23-viet-nam-21-u23-palestine-292-193665.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-giao-huu-u23-viet-nam-21-u23-palestine.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-giao-huu-u23-viet-nam-21-u23-palestine-292-193665.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2-1 U23 Palestine</span><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo t\u1ea1i c\u00fap T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:</strong><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam:\u00a0Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng; Duy M\u1ea1nh, T\u1ea5n Sinh, Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, V\u0103n Thanh, V\u0103n H\u1eadu, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng, V\u0103n To\u00e0n, V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c, Ti\u1ebfn Linh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">U23 Oman:\u00a0Mukhaini; Harthi, Rashi Al, Shayadi, Sulaman Al, Balushi, Mubarak Al, Saleh Al, Al Hidi, Ali Al, Al Sabhi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n: 2-2.</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5097","checkdouble":"193749"},{"date":"08:39 05/08","title":"L\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n tr\u1eadn Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u2013 Oman: B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh, Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng gi\u1eef b\u0103ng th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/lo-doi-hinh-ra-san-tran-viet-nam-oman-bui-tien-dung-bat-chinh-minh-vuong-giu-bang-thu-quan.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ngu\u1ed3n tin, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh c\u00f2n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1ebd gi\u1eef b\u0103ng th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</h2><h2>B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh, Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng gi\u1eef b\u0103ng th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n?</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h30 t\u1ed1i nay tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 hai t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf c\u00fap Vinaphone 2018 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra gi\u1eefa U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cho t\u1edbi l\u00fac n\u00e0y, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tr\u1eadn U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman. V\u1edbi t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt h\u01a1n l\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 sau 90 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd tung ra s\u00e2n m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c so v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ra qu\u00e2n.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tr\u1eadn U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tr\u1eadn U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/nhom-du-bi-tap-rieng-tien-dung-gan-nhu-mat-suat-bat-chinh-vao-tay-van-lam.JPG\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd ra s\u00e2n \u1edf tr\u1eadn U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman. \u1ea2nh: Zing.vn</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung g\u1ed7 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng. Ng\u00f4i sao 21 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m nay, song l\u00fac n\u00e0y anh \u0111ang g\u1eb7p kh\u00f4ng \u00edt kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh su\u1ea5t b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n anh gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m. V\u00ec v\u1eady \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Thanh H\u00f3a th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u00e0 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i ni\u1ec1m tin c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u0169ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0o s\u00e2n. B\u1ed9 ba ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u00eda tr\u00ean s\u1ebd l\u00e0 Tr\u1ecbnh V\u0103n L\u1ee3i, Hu\u1ef3nh T\u1ea5n Sinh v\u00e0 Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Chung.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a 5 c\u00e1i t\u00ean: L\u00ea V\u0103n S\u01a1n, \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng, Tri\u1ec7u Vi\u1ec7t H\u01b0ng, Tr\u1ea7n Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 Ph\u1ea1m \u0110\u1ee9c Huy s\u1ebd h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 cho h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng g\u1ed3m V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 Ti\u1ebfn Linh. \u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd, HLV Park Hang-seo c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ed9t quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00e1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi trao t\u1ea5m b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y cho ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c HLV Park Hang Seo \u2018x\u1edbi tung\u2019 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i b\u1edfi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu n\u00e0y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3 \u00f4ng ch\u1ecdn l\u1ecdc v\u00e0 t\u00ecm ra b\u1ed9 khung thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018. V\u00e0 c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u qua t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p U23 Palestine \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c cho ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i v\u00e0 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00e1c b\u00e0i t\u1eadp h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c nh\u1eb9.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h30 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay. Sau th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palestine, U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang tr\u00e0n tr\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i th\u00eam Oman. \u0110\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn, c\u00f3 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n cao.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-oman-19h30-ngay-058-co-hoi-cho-kep-phu-168-193749.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/nhan-dinh-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-oman-19h30-ngay-058-co-hoi-cho-kep-phu.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-oman-19h30-ngay-058-co-hoi-cho-kep-phu-168-193749.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman (19h30, ng\u00e0y 05/8): C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho k\u00e9p ph\u1ee5</span><br />\r\nV\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h30 t\u1ed1i nay 5/8, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 hai t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng U23 Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf gi\u1eefa U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra. V\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eefng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:\n115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5096","checkdouble":"193753"},{"date":"08:58 05/08","title":"\u201cU23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 an to\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Oman\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/3/u23-viet-nam-se-da-an-toan-truoc-oman.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t c\u1ee7a chuy\u00ean gia b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Vinh khi \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman.</h2><h2>&ldquo;U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 an to\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Oman&rdquo;</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palestine \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 hai g\u1eb7p U23 Oman. V\u1ec1 \u00fd thuy\u1ebft, Oman kh\u00f4ng h\u01a1n Palestine hay Iraq, Qatar,&hellip; nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh m\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u trong n\u0103m nay.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi g\u00f3c \u0111\u1ed9 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, chuy\u00ean gia b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Vinh cho r\u1eb1ng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u1ed9i v\u00e0ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Oman t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Vinh U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 an to\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Oman h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Vinh U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 an to\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Oman h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/HLV-Nguyen-Thanh-Vinh-U23-Viet-Nam-se-da-an-toan-truoc-Oman-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110T&nbsp;U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. \u1ea2nh: Zing.vn</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n t\u1eebng d\u1eabn d\u1eaft CLB SLNA chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean b\u00e1o D\u00e2n Tr\u00ed: &ldquo;N\u1ebfu ch\u1ec9 nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, Oman c\u00f3 v\u1ebb nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng hay nh\u01b0 Palestine, b\u1edfi Oman b\u1ecb Uzbekistan \u00e9p s\u00e2n to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u. Tuy nhi\u00ean, kh\u00f4ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd gi\u1ea5u b\u00e0i v\u00e0 gi\u1ea5u l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, b\u1edfi theo h\u00ecnh dung c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, Oman kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ebf.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Oman n\u00f3i chung mang phong c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng thu\u1ed9c khu v\u1ef1c Trung \u0110\u00f4ng, c\u0169ng nhanh, m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 kh\u00e9o. N\u00f3i g\u00ec th\u00ec n\u00f3i, v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00f9ng T\u00e2y \u00c1 v\u1eabn h\u01a1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.&nbsp;Ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean ch\u1ec9 nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00e0 coi th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 l\u1ebd s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1c chi\u1ebfn t\u1ed1c th\u1eafng, b\u1edfi \u0111\u00e1 nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd thi\u1ec7t v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m tung h\u1ebft b\u00e0i cho m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m. L\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 an to\u00e0n c\u00f3 l\u1ebd s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 c\u00e1ch b\u00e0y binh b\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, \u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Vinh d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n \u1edf tr\u1eadn Vi\u1ec7t Nam &ndash; Oman s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng kh\u00e1c nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc. V\u1ecb n\u00e0y c\u0169ng th\u1eb3ng th\u1eafn nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t, tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 gi\u1eefa nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u00e0 c\u00e1c g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u00f2n qu\u00e1 c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t v\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u00f4ng Park s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 bi\u1ec7n ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho ASIAD.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h30 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 tr\u1eadn Uzbekistan vs Palestine s\u1ebd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0o l\u00fac 16h30 c\u00f9ng ng\u00e0y. Mong b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc ch\u00fa \u00fd theo d\u00f5i.</p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/3/Highlight-Viet-Nam-vs-Palestine-.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/lo-doi-hinh-ra-san-tran-viet-nam-oman-bui-tien-dung-bat-chinh-minh-vuong-giu-bang-thu-quan-168-193753.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/lo-doi-hinh-ra-san-tran-viet-nam-oman-bui-tien-dung-bat-chinh-minh-vuong-giu-bang-thu-quan.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/lo-doi-hinh-ra-san-tran-viet-nam-oman-bui-tien-dung-bat-chinh-minh-vuong-giu-bang-thu-quan-168-193753.html\">L\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n tr\u1eadn Vi\u1ec7t Nam &ndash; Oman: B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh, Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng gi\u1eef b\u0103ng th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n?</span><br>\r\nTheo m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ngu\u1ed3n tin, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh c\u00f2n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1ebd gi\u1eef b\u0103ng th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-oman-19h30-ngay-058-co-hoi-cho-kep-phu-168-193749.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/nhan-dinh-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-oman-19h30-ngay-058-co-hoi-cho-kep-phu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-oman-19h30-ngay-058-co-hoi-cho-kep-phu-168-193749.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman (19h30, ng\u00e0y 05/8): C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho k\u00e9p ph\u1ee5</span><br>\r\nV\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h30 t\u1ed1i nay 5/8, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 hai t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng U23 Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf gi\u1eefa U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra. V\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eefng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5095","checkdouble":"193755"},{"date":"07:32 05/08","title":"Inter quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Luka Modric","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/16/inter-quyet-tam-chieu-mo-bang-duoc-luka-modric.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Inter chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Modric v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi l\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin, r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t phi v\u1ee5 bom t\u1ea5n.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nInter \u0111\u1eb7t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1edbi sao Real<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League, Luka Modric ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 &ndash; khi gi\u00fap \u0110T Croatia l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Ph\u00e1p. Sau gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n sang Inter.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean theo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 t\u1eeb b\u00e1o ch\u00ed, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 32 tu\u1ed5i th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi World Cup di\u1ec5n ra. Anh mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi, sau khi \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1 no n\u00ea danh hi\u1ec7u \u1edf T\u00e2y Ban Nha. T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn nay, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Modric v\u1eabn li\u00ean h\u1ec7 m\u1eadt thi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ed1t nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n chuy\u1ec3n sang Inter.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Inter chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Modric v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Inter chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Modric v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/Tin-chuyen-nhuong-ngay-257-MU-tong-tan-cong-Willian-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Inter chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Modric v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPh\u00eda CLB Italia c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng v\u1edbi th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV Spalleti chia s\u1ebb: &ldquo;\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c t\u00edch c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 theo chi\u1ec1u h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a Luka Modric s\u1ebd quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 CLB n\u00e0o. Nh\u01b0ng h\u00e3y \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00ean \u1ed5n. C\u00e1 nh\u00e2n t\u00f4i v\u1eabn ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c C\u0110V c\u1ee7a Inter, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 x\u1eed l\u00fd b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi Inter chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Modric, Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ra \u0111i v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 750 tri\u1ec7u euro &ndash; s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng. Nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia quy\u1ebft ch\u00ed ra \u0111i, Real Madrid s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c to\u1ea1i nguy\u1ec7n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/la-thu-cam-dong-cua-tien-ve-modric-gui-dap-co-be-5-tuoi-bi-ung-thu-188-192078.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/la-thu-cam-dong-cua-tien-ve-modric-gui-dap-co-be-5-tuoi-bi-ung-thu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/hau-truong/la-thu-cam-dong-cua-tien-ve-modric-gui-dap-co-be-5-tuoi-bi-ung-thu-188-192078.html\">L\u00e1 th\u01b0 c\u1ea3m \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Modric g\u1eedi \u0111\u00e1p c\u00f4 b\u00e9 5 tu\u1ed5i b\u1ecb ung th\u01b0</span><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ea1o c\u01a1n s\u1ed1t h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u1edf qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 v\u1edbi h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u00e1p l\u1ea1i l\u00e1 th\u01b0 c\u1ee7a fan nh\u00ed.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/thuoc-phim-hiem-ve-cau-be-luka-modric-5-tuoi-chan-cuu-giua-bay-soi-188-191375.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/thuoc-phim-hiem-ve-cau-be-luka-modric-5-tuoi-chan-cuu-giua-bay-soi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/hau-truong/thuoc-phim-hiem-ve-cau-be-luka-modric-5-tuoi-chan-cuu-giua-bay-soi-188-191375.html\">Th\u01b0\u1edbc phim hi\u1ebfm v\u1ec1 c\u1eadu b\u00e9 Luka Modric 5 tu\u1ed5i ch\u0103n c\u1eebu gi\u1eefa b\u1ea7y s\u00f3i</span><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng th\u01b0\u1edbc phim t\u01b0 li\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a Pavle Balenovic c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 29 n\u0103m ghi l\u1ea1i cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng \u1edf Croatia, n\u01a1i Luka Modric \u0111ang ph\u1ee5 gi\u00fap gia \u0111\u00ecnh ch\u0103n c\u1eebu gi\u1eefa b\u1ea7y s\u00f3i hoang d\u00e3.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5094","checkdouble":"193748"}]}